data.description: Home in Northgate district under $400k! Get your new home just in time for the holidays! This home is in a prime location, its perfectly in between downtown Newnan and Peachtree City. It takes less than 10 minutes to get to shopping, restaurants, and grocery stores. This nicely maintained home is in a quiet and friendly neighborhood. Step inside to find the two story foyer that opens up into the main living area. The living room has a brick fireplace and beautiful mantle and access to the backyard. Just off the living room is an open kitchen with plenty of counter and cabinet space, an eat in breakfast area, and bar. Walking through the kitchen is a large dinning room. The master suite is on the main floor along with the laundry room and a 1/2 bath. The master suite features trey ceilings and a walk in closet. The master bath offers a double vanity, sperate shower, and soaking tub. Upstairs is an additional 3 spacious bedrooms and full bathroom. The private backyard has a fence and patio! Garage is equipped with electric car charging outlet Come see it today!
